data.description: Nestled in a welcoming neighborhood, this delightful residence offers an excellent opportunity for a place to call home. With vaulted ceilings and thoughtful design features throughout, this home presents a comfortable and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen is adorned with a built-in china cabinet, maximizing storage space, while the adjacent dining area provides a cozy spot for meals. The living area has a fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings indoors. The owner's suite boasts of high ceilings, with lots of natural light, and a large walk-in closet. Not to mention serenity awaits in your soaking tub overlooking the luscious backyard. Downstairs, the finished bonus rooms offer flexibility and potential, with the option of a 4th bedroom, complete with an adjoining full bath. This home offers ample space for relaxation and privacy. Step outside to discover a spacious, fenced backyard, ideal for outdoor activities, and gatherings. Relax and enjoy the serene surroundings from the back deck, overlooking the beautiful Georgia landscape. Additional features include a newer roof, providing peace of mind for years to come, and the convenience of no HOA fees. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this charming house your new home. Schedule a showing today and envision the possibilities that await
